import { Box } from '@material-ui/core';

const Logo = () => (
  <Box display="flex">
    <Box
      component="span"
      m={0}
      color="#209E91"
      fontWeight="fontWeightLight"
      fontFamily="Monospace"
      fontSize="h4.fontSize"
    >
      KDB
    </Box>
    <Box
      component="span"
      m={0}
      color="#FFFFFF"
      fontWeight="fontWeightLight"
      fontFamily="Monospace"
      fontSize="h4.fontSize"
    >
      STUDIO
    </Box>
  </Box>
);

export default Logo;
